---
title: Low & Slow Madras-Style Chicken Curry with Carrot Couscous & Pickled Onion Salad
description: Spice up your dinner game with this slow-cooker masterpiece! Tender, aromatic chicken is paired with fluffy carrot-studded couscous and a tangy pickled onion and radish salad for a burst of flavour in every bite. It’s melt-in-your-mouth comfort with a vibrant twist!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
